flowchart TD
    U([User]) --> SP1[Service Provider 1\nCRM App]
    U --> SP2[Service Provider 2\nHR Portal]
    U --> SP3[Service Provider 3\nDev Tools]

    SP1 -- No local session\nRedirect to IdP --> IDP
    SP2 -- No local session\nRedirect to IdP --> IDP
    SP3 -- No local session\nRedirect to IdP --> IDP

    IDP[Identity Provider\nOkta / Azure AD / Keycloak]

    IDP --> SESSION{Active SSO\nsession?}
    SESSION -- Yes --> ISSUE[Issue token / assertion\nfor requested SP]
    SESSION -- No --> LOGIN[Show login screen]
    LOGIN --> AUTHN[Authenticate user]
    AUTHN --> SSO_CREATE[Create SSO session]
    SSO_CREATE --> ISSUE

    ISSUE --> SP1_GRANT[SP1 grants access]
    ISSUE --> SP2_GRANT[SP2 grants access]
    ISSUE --> SP3_GRANT[SP3 grants access]

    IDP --> USERSTORE[(User Directory\nLDAP / AD / DB)]
